<figure xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="fig_4"><head></head><label></label><figDesc>Fig. 4a. The spectrum of ε1(ω) for Sc2CdS4 and Y2CdS4 compounds start at low frequency with</figDesc></figure>
